The paper deals with the design of robust linear precoders for the massive MIMO downlink with imperfect CSI, which is a problem in wireless communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves modeling statistical CSI, which falls under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of minorize-maximize algorithm and deterministic equivalent method suggests the paper may also belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper deals with massive MIMO, which is a subfield of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves optimization algorithms, which is a topic in cs.LG (Machine Learning).
